  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Blood gas analysis were routinely monitor every 4 hours in our surgical cardiac intensive
      care unit (SICU). These luxury investigations waste the resources. Therefore we develop a
      pathological- based guideline for arterial blood gas analysis in patients after cardiac
      surgery. We test the guideline for its safety and efficacy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
